has been used in comparison to our old TS, hence the HDTS tag. Now, source was pretty whacked
out, had way too much brightness added to it, colours were a mess, had hardcoded subtitles
and borders. We cropped off the black borders, the one line of subs that were in the bottom
border and then we cropped the second line of subs which didn't take much off the bottom of
the video at all, so they are all gone now. We then gave it some lovin', fixed the colours,
resized and took it down to XviD. Man there's going to be tons of versions out from this source,
but here's your nice 700mb XviD anyway. This will probably be the last Capt'Mercia you'll see from
us until retail drops I guess...

